{"badges":["TM31","TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place a large bowl onto mixing bowl lid and weigh almonds and 500 g of the water into it. Set aside.","Place rice and cinnamon quill into mixing bowl and mill <nobr>25 sec\/speed 10<\/nobr>. Transfer into bowl with almonds and cover with plastic wrap. Place into refrigerator for 10-12 hours. Clean and dry mixing bowl.","Place sugar, remaining 500 g water and reserved soaked almonds into mixing bowl and blend <nobr>1 min\/speed 6<\/nobr>, until completely smooth.","Line a fine-mesh sieve with two layers of muslin cloth or a nut milk bag and place over a jug.  Transfer mixture into lined sieve and squeeze any remaining pulp to extract as much liquid as possible. Discard leftover pulp.","Divide horchata between 4 glasses and add ice. Dust with ground cinnamon before serving immediately."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["160 g blanched almonds (see Tips)","1000 g water","100 g long grain white rice","1 cinnamon quill","50 g raw sugar","ice cubes, to serve","ground cinnamon, for dusting"]}],"id":"r105738","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-qPG1OOHujek\/XZanBDa1N4I\/AAAAAAAAg40\/siW0PRCIw6w8I5KmCh-g31k5kUB-RLinACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_-mVOz1ZtY-j5YNDr.png","title":"Horchata","publishedAt":"2016-06-19T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"9.4 g","fat":"22 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"34.4 g","calories":"1578.3 kJ \/ 375.8 kcal"},"usefulItems":"fine-mesh sieve, glasses, large bowl, plastic wrap, large jug, nut milk bag or 2 muslin cloths, refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["You can substitute almonds with whole or slivered almonds which have already been blanched.","If not serving immediately, place into refrigerator. Slight separation may occur, so stir prior to serving."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","24h 10m","4 portions"]}